This article explains how to install and configure IntelliJ IDEA for use with [[ImageJ]] development. Directions correspond to IntelliJ IDEA 11.1, and may need adjustment for other versions.

== Install and configure IDEA ==

=== Setting up IDEA on Windows ===

==== Install Java Development Kit ====

Download and install JDK 6 from the [http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/ Java web site].

==== Install IDEA ====

Download and install IDEA from the [http://www.jetbrains.com/idea/download/ IDEA web site].

=== Setting up IDEA on Mac OS X ===

==== Install IDEA ====

Download and install IDEA from the [http://www.jetbrains.com/idea/download/ IDEA web site].

=== Setting up IDEA on Linux ===

